{
  "stem": "11671.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we put together 15 of us-- 15 of the people in the kibbutz put together pennies that we earned by going out and doing chores, and scrubbing, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put together their pennies in order to send a telegram.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I sent the telegram to Harold in Chicago-- you had to put down your return address.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wouldn't send a telegram with-- so that's when he finally got my address.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got a telegram back saying that, OK, I got your letter, so now I have your address.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I will write.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's how we established, but-- and in Cyprus, the British correspondents were coming in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I smuggled-- no, I didn't have to really smuggle-- I gave him a letter telling him that I am trying to meet my fiance from America.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he  was supposed to be there already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he delivered the letter to Harold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we finally-- In Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Palestine-- that I was already in Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before then, we were corresponding in Europe, when I was first corresponding in Cyp-- and then Brivio-- not in Cyp-- in Salzburg, but in Brivio.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have a whole stack of letters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still have them all that he wrote to me and I wrote back to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our romance was 18 months before we got married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw him next when we were-- when I arrived in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The British--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not on Cyprus, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Cyprus, they gave us three certificates.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our group of 42 were allowed to let three people leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they let me leave because they knew Harold was waiting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when I got to-- I got to Palestine with this one couple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were in camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
